    <p>
        An Excel template is read by XlsIO and an invoice is generated for the given invoice
        ID; this is done by fetching data corresponding to the particular ID from the Northwind
        database. Price, total, and other calculations are done with simple formulas using
        Essential XlsIO.
    </p>
    <br />
    <p>
        Click the button to view an Excel spreadsheet generated by Essential XlsIO. 
        Please note that Microsoft Excel Viewer or Microsoft Excel is required to view the resultant document.
    </p>
